innerHtml: In Game Maker Toolkit's 2024 Patreon Jam, I made a game called "The Assembly Line". This was my second game jam, and being a week-long jam I spent quite a bit of time working on it after work during the week. I created a "How I Made" video that you can watch below, or at the link above which covers the journey more in-depth.
